    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the body panels are perfectly straight with no dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring leather upholstery that remains supple and an interior that still smells new. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions perfectly, backed by a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained to the highest possible standard.",
