    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in great shape and has been well-loved, offering a smooth and reliable ride for its next owner. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice that looks sharp and performs beautifully on the road\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a high-quality car at a sensible price!",
