    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents the highest standard of care and maintenance. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior still carries that new-car feel with pristine upholstery and fully functional electronics. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience with a complete service history documented from day one. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
